title: The Andrew Luck Ripple Effect, Where to Draft Todd Gurley, and the Fantasy Football Hall of Fame | The Dantasy Football Podcast
description:
Danny Kelly, Danny Heifetz, and Craig Horlbeck break down the fantasy implications of Andrew Luck’s retirement (4:30), discuss where to draft Todd Gurley (24:30), and introduce The Ringer’s Fantasy Football Hall of Fame (37:30).
